column4:
Lynda and I join millions across America in praying for 
@POTUS and @FLOTUS, and all of those impacted by the coronavirus.

I hope my fellow Oklahomans join me in continuing to follow @CDCgov guidelines of washing your hands, wearing a mask, and practicing social distancing.

Just like our communities small businesses, rural hospitals are also feeling the economic pressure of COVID-19.

@RepJasonSmith's Saving Rural Hospitals from Closure Act would help keep our rural hospitals open and ensure no one loses access to healthcare.
https://t.co/bsRnmvG2h3

On Tuesday, @OKcommerce launched Phase 2 of the Oklahoma Business Relief Program.

@OKcommerce and the OBRP are working hard to help local businesses across the state overcome the economic challenges of COVID-19. 

Learn more ‚Üì https://t.co/pTRv9egeSN

